trans-unit.source: Defines a rectangular brush with a hatch style, a foreground color, and a background color.
trans-unit.target: 사각형 브러시를 해치 스타일, 전경 색 및 배경 색을 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: A hatch pattern is made from two colors: one defined by the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.BackgroundColor%2A>, which fills the background and one for the lines that form the pattern over the background defined by the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.ForegroundColor%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 빗살 무늬 두 가지 색에서 만들어진: 정의한 하나는 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.BackgroundColor%2A>를 채운 백그라운드에 정의 된 배경 위에 패턴을 형성 하는 줄에 대 한 하나는 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.ForegroundColor%2A>속성.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.ForegroundColor%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.BackgroundColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.HatchStyle%2A> property defines what type of pattern the brush has and can be any value from the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.HatchStyle%2A>패턴 형식을 브러시의 및 사용할 수 있는 모든 값을 정의 하는 속성은 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle>열거형.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle> </xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.HatchStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: There are more than fifty elements in the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 에&50; 개 이상의 요소가 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle>열거형.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle>
